snippet.title: Diana and Roma Pretend Play School & Eat not Healthy food
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma pretend to play school. At a break, children do not want to eat healthy food and eat fast food. But this is not healthy food for children. Diana has a stomach ache. The doctor tells the girl what food is good for children.
